lead_paragraph: The U.S. men's national soccer team will play their first friendly against Cuba in 69 years when they meet in Havana's Estadio Pedro Marrero on Oct. 7, U.S. Soccer said on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Soccer: U.S. to Meet Cuba in First Friendly in 69 Years
